Titolo: Angband (video game)

Anno: 1990

Descrizione: Angband is a dungeon-crawling roguelike computer game derived from Umoria.  It is based on the writings of J. R. R. Tolkien, in which Angband is the fortress of Morgoth.  The current version of Angband is available for all major operating systems, including Unix, Windows, Mac OS X, and Android. It's identified as one of the "major roguelikes" by John Harris.

Genere: Roguelike

Valutazione: N/A
